vote.title: A resolution approving the Dallas Fort Worth International Airport Board granting Oncor Electric Delivery Company a permanent easement for +/- 3.941 acres at the Airport’s Northwest property to build and maintain electrical infrastructure - Financing: No cost consideration to the City
